Q2. How do you automate ML testing?
I treat model evaluation as a test suite — golden datasets, synthetic data generation, metric assertions, and regression comparisons are integrated into CI/CD pipelines. Deployments are blocked if metrics regress beyond defined error budgets.

Q3. How do you test OCR / NLP pipelines?
I validate OCR quality via CER/WER metrics, NLP extraction via field-level precision/recall, and robustness using distorted image variants. I also test workflow routing based on confidence thresholds.

Q4. How do you test PII masking?
I use adversarial injection of synthetic PII patterns and assert zero false negatives. Masking accuracy is treated as a hard compliance gate.

